<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invite Friends</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            /* Center align contents */
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .invite-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #ff6600;
            /* Change button color */
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .invite-button:hover {
            background-color: #cc5500;
            /* Darker color on hover */
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="path/to/your/logo.png" alt="Your Logo" style="max-width: 200px;">
        <h1>Join Our Chat Community!</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= recipientName %>,</p>
        <p>We're thrilled to invite you to join our vibrant chat community! Connect with friends, share moments, and
            engage in meaningful conversations.</p>
        <p>To join, simply click the button below:</p>
        <a href="<%= inviteLink %>" class="invite-button">Join Now</a>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>
            <%= currentUser %>
        </p> <!-- Insert user's name here -->
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2024 VChatApp | All rights reserved
    </div>
</body>

</html>